{"tid":2451543,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"女子前年倒斃貼滿道符西貢村屋 中醫師涉謀殺 死者母今被控協助及教唆非禮罪 將轉介高等法院","createTime":"2021-03-18T07:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T09:11:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b86c3b3e7a370a41e71ad37743c59caf0de99582","tid":2451543,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:36:43.000Z","msg":"21歲女子前年被發現倒斃於西貢一間貼滿「道符」的村屋內，女子身上有多處瘀傷，事後警方拘控49歲中醫師謀殺。案件至今再有新進展，警方落案起訴女子的53歲母親，控以一項協助及教唆猥䙝侵犯罪。案件今於觀塘裁判法院提堂，被告暫時毋須答辯，案件押後至3月29日於東區法院再訊，屆時兩案將合併並轉介高等法院，控方表示不排除會向中醫師加控其他控罪。<br />\n<br />\n馬姓被告（53歲）報稱為家庭主婦，控罪指她於前年8月中某日，在西貢龍尾村一村屋內，協助及教唆張子材猥䙝侵犯X。<br />\n<br />\n涉案中醫師張子材（50歲）被控於2019年9月1日在西貢龍尾村謀殺女子X，案發當年已被控提堂。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者與父母、張及張的女徒弟同住。死者父親於2019年9月2日早上，發現死者失去知覺，於是報警，其後死者被證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/Y2PKGFDXSVA35PQ5XHREIL4ED4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2FY2PKGFDXSVA35PQ5XHREIL4ED4%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2bQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=b2e25c22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2FY2PKGFDXSVA35PQ5XHREIL4ED4%2F&h=9622ccb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/Y2PKGFDXSVA35PQ5XHREIL4ED4/</a>"},{"pid":"d49b55805b8330269d82591fb44d40fb307dd31d","tid":2451543,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8c278f6839f2bdf114b6096cc4eca7694e3498","tid":2451543,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:45:53.000Z","msg":"手joke<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1144a5a8bdd4974940179fceb2c60388e04a72da","tid":2451543,"uid":49329,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:47:13.000Z","msg":"白痴老母+神棍，害死自己個女"},{"pid":"4539d12bd0f1e96961e6493dea2d2f72481f9957","tid":2451543,"uid":187,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:47:35.000Z","msg":"831翌日發現"},{"pid":"28143d78d46b90875a57242f214b4041637a85a7","tid":2451543,"uid":392446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4539d12bd0f1e96961e6493dea2d2f72481f9957","tid":2451543,"uid":187,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:47:35.000Z","msg":"831翌日發現"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:48:28.000Z","msg":"fuck the popo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ced8e544460c406cd05d7a2a186feac4563ef30","tid":2451543,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:49:49.000Z","msg":"神棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fc9a205f699d15d46400a5bfe38cb992410d0c","tid":2451543,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:54:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1961714/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1961714/page/1</a><br />\n[香港警魔]黃大仙懷疑有手足被自殺與降魔棍事件<br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得降魔棍殺人事件<br />\n<br />\n有個智障女仔死左,21歲女<br />\n狗方聲稱係同住父母道士四人涉用降魔棍打撚死條女以謀殺拘捕<br />\n<br />\n但<br />\n<span class=\"red\">1大量親共報章無故del相關報導</span><br />\n2謀殺案竟然無跟進消息<br />\n<strong>3呢單野剛好係831後發生, 9月2日</strong><br />\n4 就我所知無咩法器係棍, 警棍就警察部大把, 係降魔棍定降魔黑棍就大家自己研究<br />\n5 棄養都有合法方式, 如果唔鐘意個女一早可送走根本不用殺人,比個女獨住一層擺明好錫<br />\n<strong>6 tvb幫手屈死者家人, 但堆符明顯係printer剛print,就算係神棍都唔會犯呢種低能錯誤</strong>"},{"pid":"d4396e8390acc21b12a5ef7ab9c0927abd22117e","tid":2451543,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:55:31.000Z","msg":"何老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff009d6595f751afe27bddb6e4a1700586fdbce","tid":2451543,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:57:55.000Z","msg":"有可能係迫個女人誣告中醫師<br />\n你唔制就屈埋你兩公婆殺人<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">荃灣警局輪姦案,納粹法院簽搜查令恐嚇受害人就證明我的推測</span>"},{"pid":"b58e352e17dd4dcf9c17e8a3225f4de9eeb0858e","tid":2451543,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4396e8390acc21b12a5ef7ab9c0927abd22117e","tid":2451543,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:55:31.000Z","msg":"何老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:58:00.000Z","msg":"白蛇浸酒  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08572d9e84a19f60588bcadfd72f3c2c4ca08517","tid":2451543,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:59:30.000Z","msg":"邪教野就算係性交轉運,食古怪野香港傳媒都不停炒花生<br />\n呢單死埋人竟然大量親共報章無故del相關報導<br />\n<br />\n姐係班媒體高層下令壓CASE"},{"pid":"699a11a9e3d75cf5e63299f3667b1ed5033f736d","tid":2451543,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"教人侵犯自己個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c6177ef910e27794531babd0cd80c1dc139035","tid":2451543,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b86c3b3e7a370a41e71ad37743c59caf0de99582","tid":2451543,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:36:43.000Z","msg":"21歲女子前年被發現倒斃於西貢一間貼滿「道符」的村屋內，女子身上有多處瘀傷，事後警方拘控49歲中醫師謀殺。案件至今再有新進展，警方落案起訴女子的53歲母親，控以一項協助及教唆猥䙝侵犯罪。案件今於觀塘裁判法院提堂，被告暫時毋須答辯，案件押後至3月29日於東區法院再訊，屆時兩案將合併並轉介高等法院，控方表示不排除會向中醫師加控其他控罪。<br />\n<br />\n馬姓被告（53歲）報稱為家庭主婦，控罪指她於前年8月中某日，在西貢龍尾村一村屋內，協助及教唆張子材猥䙝侵犯X。<br />\n<br />\n涉案中醫師張子材（50歲）被控於2019年9月1日在西貢龍尾村謀殺女子X，案發當年已被控提堂。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者與父母、張及張的女徒弟同住。死者父親於2019年9月2日早上，發現死者失去知覺，於是報警，其後死者被證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/Y2PKGFDXSVA35PQ5XHREIL4ED4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2FY2PKGFDXSVA35PQ5XHREIL4ED4%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2bQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=b2e25c22\" data-ef-